{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"99709-fa-di-yu-mi-shu","title":"法蒂与蜜树","description":"对于法蒂， 一个非常努力完成她所被交代的事的一个小女孩， 每天都是一个新的开始。 在这个故事中，法蒂学到了攀爬树有可能会导致麻烦。法蒂和蜜树是基于在加纳北部长大的女孩的真实冒险经验。","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jala Community"],"illustrators":["Therson  Boadu"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/99709-fa-di-yu-mi-shu"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90633/size3/725605a3cf6c390d5f035cd03c89fe2f.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90633/size6/725605a3cf6c390d5f035cd03c89fe2f.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63238/size6/62d68d87369f932b6a10a54eb43b26dc.jpg","text":"法蒂是个小女孩像风一样的奔跑，喜欢笑，非常努力的完成她所被交代的事。","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63239/size6/f85903026087c2796eb76733afedec8d.jpg","text":"有一天，法蒂和父亲一起骑自行车到农场去拔一些杂草。","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63240/size6/9554b95ff60c6845b8125a960de9472b.jpg","text":"法蒂很快就觉得累。\n法蒂说：“爸爸，我很热，也很累。 我可以去芒果树下坐一会儿吗？\n”\n父亲说：“好吧法蒂，你可以去那里坐一会儿。 但是，今天请不要爬树。\n”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63241/size6/aba28b8cf361c877d43d17bd321ed8b6.jpg","text":"法蒂坐在芒果树下。\n法蒂抬起头来看一看。\n她看到一个...... 两个... 三个熟的芒果！","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63242/size6/c5851fd729797830c9598573962a3b82.jpg","text":"法蒂转头看一下她的父亲。 他很忙，没有在关注她。 法蒂悄悄地开始爬上芒果树。\n法蒂想，“我要坐在那大树枝上。 这里是一个能休息和吃很多很多熟芒果的好地方。\n”\n所以她坐下开始吃了。","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63243/size6/6eabbc9c806574055e12a570f98ebcb4.jpg","text":"吃完芒果后，法蒂爬下来......\n又看到另一棵树。\n 这棵树的树皮上滴下了棕色的东西。","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63244/size6/08554ab7d28eb60b28ba52617163c4a0.jpg","text":"是蜂蜜！ 法蒂特别爱吃蜂蜜。 但她不喜欢蜜蜂。 法蒂抬起头，看到一只小蜜蜂。\n法蒂心里想，“只有一只小蜜蜂。 就算我爬上树找蜂蜜，他不会伤害我的。”","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63245/size6/1a9ad762e361035f8cd8584975ea926f.jpg","text":"法蒂看一下她的父亲。\n他没在看法蒂。\n所以法蒂爬到了树的最高点，从一个深洞中取出了蜂蜜。","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63246/size6/eea9630cdea2da5991df897640042334.jpg","text":"法蒂想，“我要坐在那大树枝上。 这里是一个休息和吃很多很多甜蜂蜜的好地方。”\n所以她坐下来开始吃了。","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63247/size6/14fe798d6dafbd86441b8f767612d524.jpg","text":"她吃完蜂蜜后，法蒂爬下树。\n然后她看到了蜜蜂。\n这么多只蜜蜂！\n嗡嗡！ 嗡嗡！ 嗡嗡！\n她尽快跑走。","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63248/size6/79aa419026201c17509453835cccfbf7.jpg","text":"法蒂跑向她的父亲。\n法蒂喘着粗气。\n父亲说，“法蒂，你去过哪里？”\n法蒂不想说她去过哪里。","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63249/size6/f483dd178d703b16596309ca5ac0ed47.jpg","text":"所以，她就说，“看，爸爸，我有一个芒果。 你想吃吗？”\n父亲说：“不，谢谢你，法蒂。 我们现在得回家了。 很快就会下雨了。”","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63250/size6/1d880fbef74e5deec0cb8a35cf6671e7.jpg","text":"回家的路上，法蒂坐在自行车上，在她父亲身后。 开始下雨了。","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63252/size6/ec1455884b3a40573ec0b0c7c938767d.jpg","text":"父亲自行车骑太快了。\n自行车控制不了了。 啪！","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63253/size6/579a44d9351eb7f9868f02b1dba34d2b.jpg","text":"自行车落在法蒂的腿上。","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63254/size6/cd8b7dafdfff44b76f0788fbaa2b7c81.jpg","text":"17/19","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63255/size6/821db9126b03bea59cf00aef1a4b5459.jpg","text":"在家里，母亲和奶奶问候了在农场过的一天。\n父亲说：“法蒂爬上了一棵树。”\n“爸爸自行车骑太快了，害它落在我的腿上”，法蒂说。","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/63256/size6/3dd70f469869625c9870aa5b15ea1b72.jpg","text":"“哦，可怜，可怜的法蒂”，母亲说。\n“可怜，可怜的法蒂，” 奶奶说。 我们必须好好照顾你的腿。\n而他们就照顾了。\n故事就这么结束了。","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":18,"words":68}}